    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@paales, have you considered using the connectors of InstantSearch.js and wrapping them in web components yourself? Another option is also to wrap the components used here. \r\n\r\nThe reason we don't (yet) offer web components by default is because the support level is lower than what we currently offer, and we haven't gotten the question very often. \r\n\r\nWhat have you tried so far? I'd like to take a look to see how it would be possible to wrap correctly",
