    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Our widgets will always need to be wrapped inside a `ais-instant-search` widget for Vue, because it relies on the component tree for URL reconciliation, for a multi-root solution; InstantSearch.js is better @zagreusinoz. \r\n\r\nCan you list what you already have made so we can help out to see how it could be possible?",
